"**7 cibles** â macOS, iOS, Android, Windows, Linux, Web et WebAssembly Ã  "
"partir du mÃŠme code source."

#: src/introduction.md:28
msgid ""
"**Familiar ecosystem** â Use npm packages like `fastify`, `mysql2`, `redis`,"
" `bcrypt`, `lodash`, and more â compiled natively."
msgstr ""
"**ÃcosystÃĻme familier** â Utilisez des paquets npm comme `fastify`, "
