"Alternate-Screen-Buffer) (so your scrollback isn't polluted), captures raw-"
"mode keypresses, and re-renders only the cells that changed between frames. "
"The cell grid is a packed `Vec<Cell>` so an 80Ã24 terminal fits in ~15 KB â "
"well within L2."
msgstr ""
"`perry/tui` entre dans le [buffer d'ÃĐcran alternatif](https://invisible-"
"island.net/xterm/ctlseqs/ctlseqs.html#h2-The-Alternate-Screen-Buffer) du "
"terminal (afin de ne pas polluer votre dÃĐfilement), capture les frappes en "
"mode brut, et ne re-rend que les cellules ayant changÃĐ entre les frames. La "
"grille de cellules est un `Vec<Cell>` compact, donc un terminal 80Ã24 tient "
"en ~15 Ko â bien dans le L2."

#: src/tui/overview.md:18
