#: src/tui/overview.md:56
msgid ""
"`run(component)` enters the alt screen, enables raw mode on stdin, spawns a "
"reader thread, and loops: reset hook index â call the component closure â "
"diff the returned widget tree against the front buffer â emit minimal ANSI "
