"HTTP/2 should reach for `node:http2`'s `createSecureServer` (which always "
"advertises `[h2, http/1.1]`)."
msgstr ""
"`key` et `cert` sont des chaÃŪnes PEM (clÃĐs PKCS#8 / RSA / EC + chaÃŪnes "
"multi-certificats toutes acceptÃĐes). ALPN utilise par dÃĐfaut `http/1.1` "
"uniquement â les programmes souhaitant HTTP/2 doivent utiliser "
"`createSecureServer` de `node:http2` (qui annonce toujours `[h2, "
"http/1.1]`)."

#: src/stdlib/http.md:92
msgid "`http2.createSecureServer({ key, cert }, handler)`"
msgstr "`http2.createSecureServer({ key, cert }, handler)`"

#: src/stdlib/http.md:94
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
