#: src/system/audio_module.md:113
msgid ""
"**Preload, decode once.** `loadSound` decodes a file to a single shared PCM "
"buffer. Every subsequent `play()` of that sound schedules the same buffer â "
"no re-decode, no second allocation. 1MB WAV = 1MB in RAM no matter how many "
"times you play it."
msgstr ""
"**PrÃĐchargez, dÃĐcodez une seule fois.** `loadSound` dÃĐcode un fichier vers "
"un buffer PCM partagÃĐ unique. Chaque `play()` suivant de ce son planifie le "
"mÃŠme buffer â pas de re-dÃĐcodage, pas de second allocation. 1Mo WAV = 1Mo en"
" RAM, quel que soit le nombre de lectures."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:117
msgid ""
"**Voice pool.** Voices are preallocated and recycled. The hot path through "
"`play()` is one indexed table read plus a `scheduleBuffer` call. No malloc, "
"no string lookup."
msgstr ""
"**Pool de voix.** Les voix sont prÃĐ-allouÃĐes et recyclÃĐes. Le chemin "
"critique de `play()` consiste en une lecture de table indexÃĐe plus un appel "
"`scheduleBuffer`. Pas de malloc, pas de recherche de chaÃŪne."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:120
msgid ""
"**One shared audio graph.** A single `AVAudioEngine` (Apple) / "
"`AudioContext` (Web) drives every sound. Bus volume / mute / solo are O(1) "
"on a mixer node, not a walk over voices."
msgstr ""
"**Un seul graphe audio partagÃĐ.** Un unique `AVAudioEngine` (Apple) / "
"`AudioContext` (Web) pilote tous les sons. Le volume, le mute et le solo "
"d'un Bus sont O(1) sur un nÅud de mixage, sans parcours de l'ensemble des "
"voix."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:123
msgid ""
"**Streaming for big files only.** Pass `stream: true` to `loadSound` for "
"music or files >2MB â Perry reads chunks from disk as the voice consumes "
"them, so a 60-minute track doesn't occupy 60MB of RAM."
