#: src/widgets/configuration.md:21
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"Widget({\n"
"    kind: \"TopSitesWidget\",\n"
"    displayName: \"Top Sites\",\n"
"    description: \"Your top performing sites\",\n"
"    supportedFamilies: [\"systemSmall\", \"systemMedium\"],\n"
"    appGroup: \"group.com.example.shared\",\n"
"\n"
